text: Nitzan () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Astrakhansky Selsoviet, Narimanovsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 120 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 40 km north-east from Buruny. == References == Category:Rural localities in Narimanovsky District
title: Nitzan, Astrakhan Oblast
